title: Obama focusing on condolences, not gun laws, in Oregon visit
text:
> Political Obama focusing on condolences, not gun laws, in Oregon visit Demonstrators wait outside of Roseburg Regional Airport for President Barack Obama's arrival, Friday, Oct. 9, 2015, in Roseburg, Ore. Angry with Obama for calling for tighter gun restrictions in the wake of last week's deadly shootings at Umpqua Community College, gun-rights activists gathered to protest the president's visit to meet with victims' families.
